{"tid":391222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大學生會：如有遮檔其他文章無署名標語海報   明早會移除","createTime":"2017-09-07T15:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T17:33:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6030954991345277f04a71e712ccf06c92f2fd84","tid":391222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"有團體到中大校園抗議，要求校方拆除宣揚「港獨」的物品。中大學生會指，如果有標語及海報沒有署名，並遮檔其他人的文章，明早會撕走。<br />\n<br />\n「珍惜群組」一批成員到掛有「港獨」橫額的中大文化廣場抗議，與部分學生對罵，保安到場分隔兩批人。有人在「民主牆」貼上標語，指中大學生會並不代表他們。<br />\n<br />\n中大校長沈祖堯在網誌表示，香港是中國一部分無可爭議，又認為校園是學習地方，不應變得政治化，呼籲同學討論政治議題時要和平理性。"},{"pid":"032d3759f3e5a1b367f2d27671b06681ddb86fe1","tid":391222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21371316_1581171888611881_5387676520949827484_n.jpg?oh=0ce61d6fa4566d66b2b0e47448d4c42d&amp;oe=5A5077DC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21371316_1581171888611881_5387676520949827484_n.jpg%3Foh%3D0ce61d6fa4566d66b2b0e47448d4c42d%26oe%3D5A5077DC&h=bf6d5ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21430333_1581171945278542_2244256330136844202_n.jpg?oh=dda1da4bd75485395dadd6195801e27e&amp;oe=5A5E5F77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21430333_1581171945278542_2244256330136844202_n.jpg%3Foh%3Ddda1da4bd75485395dadd6195801e27e%26oe%3D5A5E5F77&h=a3e19ea6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2516861da652ee43978aeac9ff3ead8d2cb6729d","tid":391222,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"出埋英文, 支那蝗唔識中文架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1db0976c828b4c7c05cdea536c6b9937abf4ab9","tid":391222,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"掛橫額有幾唔和平幾唔理性呀沈祖堯"},{"pid":"d9aee4f7360bff418e316335bceb3d399495bc11","tid":391222,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"公道講句<br />\n中大學生會係咪應該讓d位出黎？"},{"pid":"302c9e0149d8ed153e86ad0876ba1b472592989d","tid":391222,"uid":15249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掛橫額有幾唔和平幾唔理性呀沈祖堯</blockquote><br />\n校園唔講政治呢d出自政府都覺得荒謬<br />\n估唔到出自佢把口"},{"pid":"233d893f3827773aa33578fc606994c2ea456439","tid":391222,"uid":74244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"中大su個page 好撚多大陸人洗版，痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}